        "reviews_8UgFbe": {
          "type": "reviews",
          "settings": {
            "color_scheme": "background-1",
            "show_custom_bg": false,
            "custom_bg_color": "#F2EAE6",
            "corner_radius": 12,
            "border_width": 0,
            "border_color": "#C48A98",
            "avatar_alignment": "top",
            "avatar_corner_radius": 40,
            "star_color": "#C48A98",
            "stars_translate": 0,
            "checkmark_color": "#8B5E6E",
            "checkmark_icon_color": "#ffffff",
            "slider_type": "slide",
            "autoplay": false,
            "autoplay_speed": 5,
            "display_arrows": false,
            "display_dots": true,
            "author_1": "<em>Jessica M.</em> [stars]",
            "text_1": "<p>I literally use this every night while watching Netflix. The LED counter is so satisfying — I kept going just to beat my number. Already at 74 reps and I started at 12.</p>",
            "author_2": "<em>Ashley T.</em> [stars]",
            "text_2": "<p>I thought it was a gimmick. Then my abs were sore the next morning. I never left my couch. This thing is actually real.</p>",
            "author_3": "<em>Rachel K.</em> [stars]",
            "text_3": "<p>Got the Me + Partner pack. We literally compete on reps now every evening. Best $70 I've spent this year. My core is noticeably stronger after 2 weeks.</p>",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 24
          }
        },
        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What's in the box?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "redeem",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Everything you need to start your first session today:<br>✓ LunaCore Pedal Resistance Trainer<br>✓ 6 resistance tubes (adjustable intensity)<br>✓ Built-in LED rep counter (150 mAh battery)<br>✓ Non-slip foot pedals with ankle strap anchors<br>✓ 30-Day Couch Core Plan PDF (free digital bonus)<br>✓ 30-day money-back guarantee</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "faq_tab_1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the LED counter actually work?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes — it uses a 150 mAh battery and counts mechanically every time you complete a rep. No app, no Bluetooth, no setup. Just pull and watch the number go up.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "faq_tab_2": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it if I'm a complete beginner?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Absolutely. LunaCore is designed for people who haven't exercised in a while. You can start seated on a chair or sofa. The resistance is adjustable — start light, build up at your own pace. No experience needed.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "faq_tab_3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When will my order arrive?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "local_shipping",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Orders ship within 1–3 business days. Delivery takes 10–18 days to the US. You'll receive a tracking number by email as soon as your order ships.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "faq_tab_4": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if it doesn't work for me?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "favorite",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Use it for 30 days. If you don't feel a difference, contact us and we'll refund every cent. No forms, no questions, no hassle. We stand behind this product 100%.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        }
